    | 3 | TimeSlot, FreeBusyBlock, RecurrenceRule models | -- | SRP |
    | 4 | CalendarService.getFreeBusyBulk() aggregates all calendars | Service | SRP |
    | 5 | IntervalMerge / SweepLine / BruteForce find common free slots | Strategy (finding) | OCP, DIP |
    | 6 | EarliestFirst / PreferredTime / MinFragmentation ranking | Strategy (ranking) | OCP |
    | 7 | Meeting created with responses per participant + recurrence | -- | SRP |
    | 8 | Invite, calendar sync, reminder, conflict detection notified | Observer + Strategy | OCP, SRP |
    |  |  |  |  |
